258
00:24:31.815 --> 00:24:34.353
See? Money's the problem.

259
00:24:34.353 --> 00:24:35.959
Think about it.

260
00:24:37.180 --> 00:24:39.910
<i>What you want to buy is too expensive.</i>

261
00:24:39.910 --> 00:24:42.565
<i>But it's not satisfying enough
