265
00:24:50.859 --> 00:24:53.411
and hit the jackpot.

266
00:24:54.366 --> 00:24:55.568
Yes!

267
00:24:58.613 --> 00:25:01.372
People hit the jackpot
at least once in their lives.

268
00:25:02.028 --> 00:25:05.075
Then, what do you think will happen?

269
00:25:17.190 --> 00:25:19.728
Let's go to a casino first.
Bring your money.

270
00:25:20.994 --> 00:25:22.515
I have it. Let's go.

271
00:25:24.395 --> 00:25:26.728
I don't want to.

272
00:25:26.728 --> 00:25:29.208
We should visit a casino
if we're in France.

273
00:25:29.208 --> 00:25:33.487
You never wanted to go anywhere
before. What's gotten into you today?

274
00:25:33.487 --> 00:25:36.798
We'll only go once
in our lifetime. Let's go.

275
00:25:36.798 --> 00:25:39.258
That time when customers
came and played Go-stop

276
