people next door reported it, so we lost
our business license. Did you forget?

277
00:25:43.115 --> 00:25:45.921
I get goosebumps
when I think about Go-stop!

278
00:25:45.921 --> 00:25:49.988
People don't play Go-stop in
French casinos. Get up. Come out.

279
00:25:52.969 --> 00:25:54.965
