280
00:25:58.269 --> 00:25:59.782
Gosh.

281
00:26:09.007 --> 00:26:11.484
Don't drink like that.

282
00:26:12.212 --> 00:26:14.533
- Aren't you drinking?
- I don't like beer.

283
00:26:14.533 --> 00:26:15.673
Really?

284
00:26:19.183 --> 00:26:22.757
- Do you drink?
- Gosh, you're so annoying.

285
00:26:22.757 --> 00:26:24.547
