as soon as a movie came out.

305
00:27:57.400 --> 00:28:01.507
"It's PG-12. It's PG 15."

306
00:28:01.507 --> 00:28:04.283
"I can watch it with her."

307
00:28:04.283 --> 00:28:08.209
