311
00:28:19.577 --> 00:28:23.496
- You can stop talking about that.
- This is important, though.

312
00:28:25.370 --> 00:28:28.139
Na Hyun's dream was to
become a movie director.

313
00:28:28.139 --> 00:28:31.335
That's why she wanted to create a film
that would resonate with kids her age.

314
00:28:31.335 --> 00:28:34.426
