315
00:28:34.426 --> 00:28:37.276
Did you even watch what she made?

316
00:28:39.056 --> 00:28:41.510
It's too dirty to even talk about.

317
00:28:41.510 --> 00:28:44.970
But I'm sure Na Hyun wanted to
say something else...

318
00:28:44.970 --> 00:28:47.373
Talking about it is dirty.

319
00:28:47.373 --> 00:28:50.700
Erotic films are less dirty
than what she made.

320
00:28:50.700 --> 00:28:54.305
- I'll apologize on her behalf.
- That's a given.

321
00:28:54.305 --> 00:28:57.381
But I can't accept it from my standpoint.

322
00:29:03.298 --> 00:29:04.604
I...

