and jumped me.

357
00:31:10.353 --> 00:31:12.498
- Really?
- Really.

358
00:31:12.498 --> 00:31:15.622
- What about your gun?
- I had no time to shoot.

359
00:31:15.622 --> 00:31:17.757
It was already jumping toward me.

360
00:31:17.757 --> 00:31:18.941
And then?

361
00:31:18.941 --> 00:31:22.788
So I grabbed the tiger's neck
on a whim and yelled at it.

362
00:31:22.788 --> 00:31:25.149
"You son of a bitch."

363
00:31:25.149 --> 00:31:28.257
- And then...
- Keep going.

364
00:31:32.734 --> 00:31:35.930
He said, "I'm not a dog."

365
00:31:35.930 --> 00:31:38.051
It's an old story.

366
00:31:39.950 --> 00:31:43.220
- Cheers.
- I said I don't like beer.

367
00:31:44.314 --> 00:31:45.610
Really?

368
00:31:46.663 --> 00:31:48.305
Excuse me.

369
00:33:36.329 --> 00:33:42.793
<font color="#80ffff">[DF Ver] E09 The Package</font>
