372
00:35:41.082 --> 00:35:42.910
I played hooky.

373
00:35:42.910 --> 00:35:45.750
Geez, way to be a good teacher.

374
00:35:45.750 --> 00:35:49.067
Thanks for the compliment.
What about So So?

375
00:35:49.067 --> 00:35:50.868
I found her.

376
00:35:52.201 --> 00:35:54.683
- She bought me these clothes.
