384
00:36:19.384 --> 00:36:22.384
- Don't you feel safe?
- Of course.

385
00:36:23.375 --> 00:36:26.406
Is So So still pretty as always?
Is she eating properly?

386
00:36:26.406 --> 00:36:27.982
