393
00:37:16.055 --> 00:37:19.136
I wore clothes and shoes
that I never wear

394
00:37:19.136 --> 00:37:21.352
to watch a show that was too expensive.

395
00:37:21.352 --> 00:37:25.799
I treated myself for once
in my life today. Don't ruin it.

396
00:37:27.417 --> 00:37:31.388
I'm not enjoying myself here.
I'm not just fooling around with you

397
00:37:31.388 --> 00:37:34.335
after breaking up with
my girlfriend during this vacation.

398
00:37:34.335 --> 00:37:37.660
