414
00:38:32.495 --> 00:38:36.468
No, Didier and Allan are lovers.

415
00:38:40.611 --> 00:38:42.694
But they're both men.

416
00:38:42.694 --> 00:38:44.178
That's right.

417
00:38:44.178 --> 00:38:48.372
They're engaged, but they were
about to call it off, so I tried to...

418
00:38:49.131 --> 00:38:52.355
Wait, what were you thinking...

419
00:38:53.189 --> 00:38:56.948
Did I seem like someone
who'd do that with two men...

420
00:38:56.948 --> 00:39:00.754
Look here, San Ma Ru! Is that
the kind of person you take me for?

421
00:39:01.330 --> 00:39:04.591
If they're lovers,
then what are they to you?

422
00:39:04.591 --> 00:39:07.910
Don't you remember?
How did I introduce them to you?

423
00:39:07.910 --> 00:39:11.160
- As your boyfriends.
