430
00:39:32.710 --> 00:39:36.142
Not just friends, but my best...

431
00:39:37.426 --> 00:39:39.877
- Let's stop.
- I'm sorry.

432
00:39:39.877 --> 00:39:42.776
- You don't have to apologize.
- I'm really sorry.

433
00:39:44.439 --> 00:39:48.194
I didn't know that,
and thought I was a nobody to you.

434
00:39:48.194 --> 00:39:53.524
San Ma Ru, you have
the qualities that I hate the most.

435
00:39:53.524 --> 00:39:57.361
You misunderstand, hurt,
and think however you want.

436
00:39:57.361 --> 00:39:59.007
After expecting
the other person to see that

437
00:39:59.007 --> 00:40:01.216
you just form your own conclusion.

438
00:40:01.216 --> 00:40:03.227
And after finding out
it was a misunderstanding

439
00:40:03.227 --> 00:40:07.797
you still want the other person
to understand you and comfort you.

440
00:40:07.797 --> 00:40:09.602
And secondly...

441
00:40:23.718 --> 00:40:25.386
I don't even want to say it.

442
00:40:27.214 --> 00:40:28.973
