480
00:43:17.064 --> 00:43:22.645
It was all shiny with lights
flashing everywhere.

481
00:43:22.645 --> 00:43:24.524
That was unbelievably fun.

482
00:43:24.524 --> 00:43:28.232
How did I live without knowing
how fun that is?

483
00:43:34.422 --> 00:43:37.160
- Go.
